Gender

Female churn rate: 55%

Male churn rate: 38%
Insight: Women are significantly more likely to leave; the product may not meet female expectations.

Age

Older customers churn: 51%

Young & middle-aged churn: ~44%
Insight: Older customers show lower product fit or higher dissatisfaction.

Gender √ó Age

Female customers churn more across all age groups.
Business Meaning: Product experience fails to retain female customers over time.

